<h3 id='field-spawn'>Field : spawn()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_1</span>   <span class="c1">-- example entity</span>
<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_2</span>   <span class="c1">-- example entity</span>
<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_3</span>   <span class="c1">-- example entity</span>

<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">spawn1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">field</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">spawn</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="p">)</span>
<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">spawn2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">field</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">spawn</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span> <span class="p">)</span>
<span class="kd">local</span> <span class="n">spawn3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">field</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="n">spawn</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="n">new_enemy_3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>The above snippet spawns three enemies on the center column of the opponent&#39;s area.</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>field:spawn( entity, x, y )</code></p>
<h4 id='return-value'>Return Value</h4><h4 id='parameters'>Parameters</h4>
<p><code>entity</code><br>
    &emsp;<em>A pointer to the  you want to spawn.</em><br>
<strong><code>integer</code></strong> <code>x</code><br>
    &emsp;<em>The <strong>column</strong> you want to spawn the  in <strong>(from left to right)</strong>.</em><br>
<strong><code>integer</code></strong> <code>y</code><br>
    &emsp;The <strong>row</strong> you want to spawn the  in <strong>(from top to bottom)</strong>.)</p>

<aside class="warning">If you attempt to spawn an  outside of the bounds of the battlefield, it will <i>not</i> spawn at all.<br>
(i.e. <code>x < 0</code>, <code>y < 0</code>, <code>(x > field:width() - 1)</code> or <code>y > (field:height() - 1)</code>)<br>
It will return <code>AddEntityStatus.Deleted</code> if that happens.</aside>
